    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/yet74e-p1/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=619933412978852657&sectionId=619933413147149105)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"gglxmAkgFII_text","label":"gglxmAkgFII_text","default":"<p><strong>1. razlog</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsS4ONFLh0_text","label":"ggsS4ONFLh0_text","default":"<strong>Celovita podpora sklepom v eni kapsuli</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5GBcObD7o_text","label":"gg5GBcObD7o_text","default":"<p>MobiMix zagotavlja vse glavne koristi za sklepe, ki jih vaš pes potrebuje — za lažje gibanje in udobno vsakodnevno aktivnost.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggw_wXa6GDw_childItem_0","label":"ggw_wXa6GDw_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>Podpora pri šepanju</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzHVtyZFPM_childItem_0","label":"ggzHVtyZFPM_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>Podpora gibljivosti</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpw2-5EFF5_childItem_0","label":"ggpw2-5EFF5_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>Podpora pri bolečini</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggit7iRjK5C_childItem_0","label":"ggit7iRjK5C_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>Podpora elastičnosti veziva</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpTF_l9byS_childItem_0","label":"ggpTF_l9byS_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>Krepitev kosti in sklepov</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRDDjvSCfm_childItem_0","label":"ggRDDjvSCfm_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>Vlaženje sklepov</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0CXBHphcT_childItem_0","label":"gg0CXBHphcT_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>Tvorba sinovialne tekočine</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggv3E-fmKRe_childItem_0","label":"ggv3E-fmKRe_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>Obnova in zaščita hrustanca</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdHMIB0Ox2_childItem_0","label":"ggdHMIB0Ox2_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>Krepitev vezivnega tkiva</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggweTeE1Qyg_childItem_0","label":"ggweTeE1Qyg_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>Protivnetna podpora</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJVbALlEZT_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggJVbALlEZT_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/image_2.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHrWPIKr8x_text","label":"ggHrWPIKr8x_text","default":"<p><strong>2. razlog</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggoksyex6gX_text","label":"ggoksyex6gX_text","default":"<strong>Izkušnja, ki je spremenila življenje več kot 10.000 psov</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggg4SWF4olV_text","label":"ggg4SWF4olV_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(26,26,26);\"><i>\"Videl sem starejše pse z bolečim šepanjem in nizko energijo, ki so popolnoma znova pridobili mobilnost in samozavest. Psi, ki so se komaj dvignili s kavča, spet tečejo po parku.&nbsp;</i></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(26,26,26);\"><i>Psi, ki so se bali stopnic, zdaj hitijo po njih. To je ena izmed najlepših stvari, ki jih vidim v svoji praksi — in zato priporočam MobiMix lastnikom psov, ki želijo svojim starejšim psom dati še več dobrih let.\"</i></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAsb4FqZFv_label","label":"ggAsb4FqZFv_label","default":"<p><strong>Preizkusite MobiMix danes</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDrTV-a-FH_text","label":"ggDrTV-a-FH_text","default":"<p><strong>Po 3 mesecih več kot 80% lastnikov poroča o vidnih izboljšavah!</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggiurfhs7bP_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggiurfhs7bP_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/image00004_db7b8cc8-6684-47d2-980a-96f678167a77.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4NUfX84MK_text","label":"gg4NUfX84MK_text","default":"<p><strong>3. razlog</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcPkOnFry8_text","label":"ggcPkOnFry8_text","default":"<strong>Formuliran z osmimi klinično preverjenimi sestavinami</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggY9KtHiL29_text","label":"ggY9KtHiL29_text","default":"<p>Vsaka sestavina MobiMix-a je podprta z raziskavami in klinično dokazana za podporo sklepom pri psih. Razvit je s pomočjo strokovnjakov na področju veterine, farmacije in zootehnike.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Vsaka kapsula je napolnjena s hranili, ki resnično naredijo razliko.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqRpBD7OPs_text","label":"ggqRpBD7OPs_text","default":"<p>✅ <strong>GMP standardi </strong>(Good Manufacturing Practice)</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwn2WSucJ3_text","label":"ggwn2WSucJ3_text","default":"<p>✅ <strong>ISO 22000 </strong>(Varnost živil)</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-e7VC-eYz_text","label":"gg-e7VC-eYz_text","default":"<p><strong>100% naravno. Brez umetnih barvil, konzervansov ali polnil.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8tTJ2D5n4_text","label":"gg8tTJ2D5n4_text","default":"<p><i><strong>\"Res se vse živo reklamira, ampak tole deluje.\"</strong></i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBGVw3PdO5_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggBGVw3PdO5_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/hf_20260414_104511_dcf5f950-d8a5-4d49-a137-debe504cf64c.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYDV4r9ex4_text","label":"ggYDV4r9ex4_text","default":"Vsaka sestavina MobiMix-a naslavlja enega izmed treh vzrokov za propadanje sklepov:"},{"type":"html","id":"ggU7jWXEqey_text","label":"ggU7jWXEqey_text","default":"<p>Natančno izbrane naravne učinkovine, ki skupaj podpirajo sklepe, gibljivost in dolgoročno zdravje vašega psa.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzllfCcJ3m_text","label":"ggzllfCcJ3m_text","default":"<p><strong>VZROK 1: VNETJE</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9Z1IWGvs7_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg9Z1IWGvs7_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/Zelenoustna_skoljka.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVoqRZxnPx_text","label":"ggVoqRZxnPx_text","default":"Zelenoustna školjka"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWvl4A9eFw_text","label":"ggWvl4A9eFw_text","default":"<p>Naravni vir učinkovin, ki pomagajo zmanjševati vnetja, lajšati bolečine in podpirajo obnovo sklepnega hrustanca. Primerna za dolgotrajno podporo sklepom pri starejših in bolj obremenjenih psih.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJSH2Wi8-A_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggJSH2Wi8-A_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/vrazji-krempelj.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9nRmtCDAg_text","label":"gg9nRmtCDAg_text","default":"Vražji krempelj"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjR95OOVU4_text","label":"ggjR95OOVU4_text","default":"<p>Naravna pomoč pri lajšanju bolečin, togosti in oteklin v sklepih. Primeren za pse z degenerativnimi težavami gibal.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPWZ5955VJ_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggPWZ5955VJ_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/ingver.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJj1RMfeOA_text","label":"ggJj1RMfeOA_text","default":"Ingver"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTmaXjxEWs_text","label":"ggTmaXjxEWs_text","default":"<p>Pomaga zmanjševati bolečine in togost v sklepih ter podpira boljše gibanje. Pogosta izbira za dolgotrajno, naravno podporo gibal.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdtkQawE-5_text","label":"ggdtkQawE-5_text","default":"<p><strong>VZROK 2: OBRABA HRUSTANCA</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIa194ca7Y_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggIa194ca7Y_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/glukozamin.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0NUoPBbdi_text","label":"gg0NUoPBbdi_text","default":"Glukozamin"},{"type":"html","id":"ggy0f8Y8YPU_text","label":"ggy0f8Y8YPU_text","default":"<p>Ključna gradbena snov hrustanca, ki pomaga ohranjati prožnost sklepov in zmanjševati njihovo obrabo. Pomemben za pse srednjih in večjih pasem.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFKsmiT-mK_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggFKsmiT-mK_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/Hondroitin.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRtFm7jcts_text","label":"ggRtFm7jcts_text","default":"Hondroitin"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8Enee410v_text","label":"gg8Enee410v_text","default":"<p>Pomaga zadrževati vlago v hrustancu ter ohranja njegovo blažilno in zaščitno funkcijo. V kombinaciji z glukozaminom dolgoročno podpira sklepno gibljivost.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMdRPM_9dM_text","label":"ggMdRPM_9dM_text","default":"<p><strong>VZROK 3: OKSIDATIVNI STRES</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6s1mppHeH_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg6s1mppHeH_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/Kurkuma.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggipJouOqCm_text","label":"ggipJouOqCm_text","default":"Kurkuma"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtMOejyBvK_text","label":"ggtMOejyBvK_text","default":"<p>Močan naravni antioksidant, ki pomaga zmanjševati kronično vnetje in ščiti sklepna tkiva. Podpira splošno regeneracijo in gibljivost.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6D0DI0bZc_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg6D0DI0bZc_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/sipek.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHApx0sSOS_text","label":"ggHApx0sSOS_text","default":"Šipek"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmEWPG108A_text","label":"ggmEWPG108A_text","default":"<p>Vir antioksidantov, ki pomagajo zmanjševati sklepne bolečine in podpirajo gibljivost. Hkrati prispeva k splošni odpornosti organizma.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsSrFNF4B__srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggsSrFNF4B__srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/vitamin-c.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsl5YHDZ7r_text","label":"ggsl5YHDZ7r_text","default":"Vitamin C"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7z7Pf_Pav_text","label":"gg7z7Pf_Pav_text","default":"<p>Ključen za tvorbo kolagena in zdravje sklepov, vezi ter hrustanca. Pomaga upočasniti degenerativne procese in podpira regeneracijo.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gga3LpZ619e_childItem_0","label":"gga3LpZ619e_childItem_0","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#0E1111;\"><strong>Vse informacije o izdelku</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghNNyPq_VY_text","label":"gghNNyPq_VY_text","default":"<p><strong>Vsebina pakiranja</strong></p><p><strong>Oblika:</strong> kapsule</p><p><strong>Količina v pakiranju:</strong> 90 kapsul</p><p><strong>Neto vsebina:</strong> 270 g</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Kako dolgo zadostuje ena posodica?</strong><br>Trajanje uporabe je odvisno od velikosti psa:</p><p><strong>Majhni psi (0–10 kg):</strong> do <strong>3 mesece</strong></p><p><strong>Srednje veliki psi (10–20 kg):</strong> približno <strong>1,5 meseca</strong></p><p><strong>Veliki psi (20–30 kg):</strong> približno <strong>1 mesec</strong></p><p><strong>Zelo veliki psi (nad 30 kg):</strong> približno <strong>3 tedne</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Shranjevanje</strong><br>Shranjujte na <strong>hladnem in suhem mestu</strong>, zaščiteno pred vlago.<br>Hranite <strong>izven dosega otrok in živali</strong>.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTYYyNeodZ_label","label":"ggTYYyNeodZ_label","default":"<p><strong>Preizkusite MobiMix danes</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQOevY-nqq_text","label":"ggQOevY-nqq_text","default":"<p><strong>4. razlog</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggV93SgayJn_text","label":"ggV93SgayJn_text","default":"Vidni Rezultati v 2-3 Tednih ⏱️"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDDn9iTm43_text","label":"ggDDn9iTm43_text","default":"<p>Večina lastnikov psov vidi pravo izboljšanje v prvem mesecu. Najpogostejša napaka je nedoslednost — preskakovanje dni bistveno zmanjša rezultate. Uporabljajte <strong>MobiMix vsak dan za najboljše rezultate.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGydg9fhmM_text","label":"ggGydg9fhmM_text","default":"<p><strong>MobiMix deluje hitreje in dlje:</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZ7eU9-pQd_text","label":"ggZ7eU9-pQd_text","default":"<p><strong>📅&nbsp; 2-3 tedni: </strong>Lažje hodi po stopnicah, manj bolečin</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYdYHlGFF__text","label":"ggYdYHlGFF__text","default":"<p>📅&nbsp; <strong>1 mesec:</strong> Bolečine skoraj povsem izginejo, sklepi prožnejši</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnh4LWZh17_text","label":"ggnh4LWZh17_text","default":"<p><strong>📅&nbsp; 2-3 mesece:</strong> Hoja po parkih, igranje – vse lažje</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUp84xXgC-_text","label":"ggUp84xXgC-_text","default":"<p><strong>📅&nbsp; 3+ mesece:</strong> Uživa v dolgih sprehodih brez omejitev</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVlAAZ75_-_text","label":"ggVlAAZ75_-_text","default":"<p>Ne čakajte mesece v upanju. Rezultati so hitri in vidni.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVrHr5YRCk_text","label":"ggVrHr5YRCk_text","default":"<p><i><strong>\"Po treh tednih je naš Rex spet lahko skočil na kavč.</strong></i><br><i><strong>Mislila sem, da je to čudež.\"</strong></i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg05ZJN-Lz-_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg05ZJN-Lz-_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/image00002_9bfcbcfd-8a57-4638-a822-e6ac9ebe4aa5.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gggfJGewSML_text","label":"gggfJGewSML_text","default":"<p><strong>5. razlog</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOw-012NN9_text","label":"ggOw-012NN9_text","default":"<strong>Brez polnil, brez umetnih dodatkov — samo tisto, kar deluje!&nbsp;</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggg7iK8Fmhi_text","label":"ggg7iK8Fmhi_text","default":"<p><strong>MobiMix vsebuje samo tisto, kar je dokazano učinkovito — v odmerkih, ki so dovolj visoki, da resnično naredijo razliko.</strong><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(85,85,85);\"> Brez umetnih barv. Brez GMO. Brez hormonov ali antibiotikov.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Laboratorijsko testiran po serijah in proizveden v GMP-certificiranem obratu.</strong><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(85,85,85);\"> Vsaka sestavina je globalno pridobljena za maksimalno čistost in učinkovitost.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwhKj8MOMd_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggwhKj8MOMd_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/WhatsApp_Image_2026-01-21_at_16.25.06_8af0fb41-e1bb-40af-8cba-ab85430f6e17.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPhgUgUMyj_text","label":"ggPhgUgUMyj_text","default":"<p><strong>Dodaten razlog</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9YeD4iGBG_text","label":"gg9YeD4iGBG_text","default":"Če ne deluje — dobite denar nazaj. Brez vprašanj."},{"type":"html","id":"ggq_lHApLgb_text","label":"ggq_lHApLgb_text","default":"<p>Razumemo, da ste že poskusili. Že ste zapravili denar na stvareh ki niso delovale.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Če vaš pes v roku 60 dni ne vstaja lažje, ne hodi bolje, ne kaže nobene spremembe — nam napišite in vrnemo celoten znesek. Brez vprašanj. Brez zapletov.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCgba3c5V-_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggCgba3c5V-_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/image_4.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPi8uyWbQ0_text","label":"ggPi8uyWbQ0_text","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\"><strong>Klinično preizkušeno</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZNTAKjKhM_text","label":"ggZNTAKjKhM_text","default":"Klinično podprto, veterinarsko priporočeno — vsaka sestavina v dokazani količini.&nbsp;"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEeu5KEuUy_text","label":"ggEeu5KEuUy_text","default":"<p>780 mg aktivnih sestavin na kapsulo. Brez simboličnih količin. Vsaka sestavina navedena na etiketi.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>8 naravnih učinkovin. 3 mehanizmi. Vsaka v klinično učinkoviti dozi — ne sledovi ki jih uporabljajo drugi dodatki.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Razvito in proizvedeno v Evropi. GMP in ISO 22000 certificirano. 60-dnevna garancija vračila denarja — brez vprašanj, brez zapletov. Brez tveganja.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfsQhsM47O_text","label":"ggfsQhsM47O_text","default":"<strong>Zaupa mu že več kot 10.000 strank po vsej Evropi.</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFywK2mdCt_text","label":"ggFywK2mdCt_text","default":"<p><i>\"Maj bi moral biti operiran, žal pa so na isti dan operirali mene. Namreč ima kronično vnetje kolenskih sklepov. Po treh tednih jemanja MobiMixa je Maj čudežno shodil. Veterinarja vprašam, kaj sedaj to pomeni. Veterinar mi odgovori, da nima druge razlage kot da je to božji čudež. Ta božji čudež traja že leto dni in upam, da bo trajal in trajal.\"</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjkQqM963__srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggjkQqM963__srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/66803718_10213185147055949_4776463675689009152_n.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNFxsEP8o7_text","label":"ggNFxsEP8o7_text","default":"<p><strong>Branko Teršek</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggY2QwRs9lX_text","label":"ggY2QwRs9lX_text","default":"<p>12- letni ovčar</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggv5k_pawfj_text","label":"ggv5k_pawfj_text","default":"<p><i>\"Zdaj smo začeli z drugo škatlo MobiMixa. Pri našem psu so se začele vidne spremembe na boljše po treh tednih. Kuža ima osteoartritis in je pred uporabo imel velike težave kljub uporabi različnih sorodnih izdelkov. MobiMix priporočam vsem, ki se srečujejo s težavami. Pri nas gre za neverjetno izboljšanje.</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaX12NCrc2_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggaX12NCrc2_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/184792313_309577037213114_6430652014317397683_n.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggN7QefvSRE_text","label":"ggN7QefvSRE_text","default":"<p><strong>Marica Ikanović</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggteWTOyRPo_text","label":"ggteWTOyRPo_text","default":"<p>12- letni ovčar</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdpEd9x-S6_text","label":"ggdpEd9x-S6_text","default":"<p><i>\"Tole pa res pomaga. Ko nam je zmanjkalo en teden nismo dajali, se je stanje občutno poslabšalo. Običajno ne verjamem takim stvarem, tokrat pa res. Ne delam reklame ampak pišem iz izkušenj našega 14 letnega starega borderja.\"</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbupqVssSC_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggbupqVssSC_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/hf_20260414_103336_948147ac-b0fa-4f70-9742-d2125fb67dd2.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmDCYaN_Av_text","label":"ggmDCYaN_Av_text","default":"<p><strong>Mateja Roth</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUz-wnSl16_text","label":"ggUz-wnSl16_text","default":"<p>14 - letni Borderski ovčar</p>"}],
